{"tid":2448868,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國正審議有關收緊遊行集會議案，擴警權","createTime":"2021-03-16T08:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T11:00:10.000Z","uid":22054,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72cb4a37e084463c04d783138010fa9bfb853719","tid":2448868,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.trust.org/item/20210315164048-a857w/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.trust.org%2Fitem%2F20210315164048-a857w%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirMmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=4bfb2b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.trust.org/item/20210315164048-a857w/</a><br />\n如果通過，警察可以為遊行集會訂下嘈音標準同結束時間，我知好多人見到BLM D撚樣出聲就唔想理，但法例唔會只禁你唔想出現既聲音<br />\n<br />\n佢條Bill 係闊到只要警察認為遊行集會既嘈音對任何一個開緊工既人(包括領事館，甚至超市)有影響(impact)都可以施加restriction/ 終止遊行集會，或者影響到一個路人都可以施加restriction/ 終止遊行集會<br />\n<br />\n而家警方宣佈終止遊行要個示威者知道先有事，即係聽唔到，睇唔到，冇睇警察Twitter都係抗辯理由，放走既機率都唔低（控方要證明被捕人一定知），但新法例下呢D都變成參與者責任<br />\n<br />\n以下係前首相Theresa May對議案既發言:<br />\nI absolutely accept that the police have got certain challenges, for example when people glue themselves to vehicles or the gates of Parliament.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;But freedom of speech is an important right in our democracy, however annoying or uncomfortable sometimes that might be, and I know there will be people who will have seen scenes of protest and will have said, &lsquo;why isn&rsquo;t the Government doing something?&rsquo;, to which the answer in many cases may simply be because we live in a democratic, free society.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;So I do worry about the potential unintended consequences of some of the measures in the Bill which have been drawn quite widely. Protests have to be under the rule of law, but the law has to be proportionate."},{"pid":"4e36b818f2751c20b8f7bd92b530bf4011671cc0","tid":2448868,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:17:51.000Z","msg":"做乜負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab300749d0bcd7d68142820811fbf7a25ab8bce","tid":2448868,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"倫敦可以一星期7日都有遊行集會，只係唔同地方唔同議題，但呢個係民主自由既可貴之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e60ab1d722e887f4052083d49520971b1cf32bf","tid":2448868,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844d4110b85de7685ec82a7cc1e2687d581b0092","tid":2448868,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fab300749d0bcd7d68142820811fbf7a25ab8bce","tid":2448868,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"倫敦可以一星期7日都有遊行集會，只係唔同地方唔同議題，但呢個係民主自由既可貴之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"但佢可以隨時武力驅散咁解<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player%3FnewsId%3D427377&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj9ivmuwrTvAhUECqYKHScJBGsQtwIwBHoECAsQAg&amp;usg=AOvVaw3GJWCm62AGBvcH68Gt6fSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%253FnewsId%253D427377%26ved%3D2ahUKEwj9ivmuwrTvAhUECqYKHScJBGsQtwIwBHoECAsQAg%26usg%3DAOvVaw3GJWCm62AGBvcH68Gt6fSo&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirMmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=7c30452b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%253FnewsId%253D427377%26ved%3D2ahUKEwj9ivmuwrTvAhUECqYKHScJBGsQtwIwBHoECAsQAg%26usg%3DAOvVaw3GJWCm62AGBvcH68Gt6fSo&h=d570744b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player%3FnewsId%3D427377&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj9ivmuwrTvAhUECqYKHScJBGsQtwIwBHoECAsQAg&amp;usg=AOvVaw3GJWCm62AGBvcH68Gt6fSo</a>"},{"pid":"c934500109aa272f15dbed23ac6d29fd2fabcba4","tid":2448868,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c